main event: A resident of Orangevale, California, observed a bright white object traveling in the night sky, which was reported as a UFO.
interesting points: The object traveled from North to South in a straight flight below the stars,The total observation lasted for 23 minutes,The object appeared larger than an automobile and had no visible wings or propulsion, The officer observing the object reported it had an exhaust trail, and it faded out in approximately 2 1/2 minutes.
sighted object: a bright white object resembling a star
